{"title":"在风雨中闯","authors":["邹德学"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":8,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"在风雨中闯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军某部战士  邹德学"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴雨倾，霹雷炸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"练兵号声嘀嗒嗒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连长下命令："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“出发！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走，到风雨中闯呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背包捆又捆，腰带扎又扎；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席语录揣在怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天不怕，地不怕！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花盆里长不成大树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庭院里练不出骏马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要练硬功夫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到风雨中摸爬滚打。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卧泥水，怀天下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪膛刀尖火辣辣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杀声震碎风和雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀光迎来满天霞。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}